NAME
    Perinci::Sub::Property::hide_args - Hide arguments

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.01 of
    Perinci::Sub::Property::hide_args (from Perl distribution
    Perinci-Sub-Property-hide_args), released on 2014-06-15.

SYNOPSIS
     # in function metadata
     hide_args => [qw/arg1 arg2/],

DESCRIPTION
    This property can hide some arguments from function, so they are assumed
    to not exist.

SEE ALSO
    Perinci

HOMEPAGE
    Please visit the project's homepage at
    <https://metacpan.org/release/Perinci-Sub-Property-hide_args>.

